{"type": "article", "id": 16742, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-29T07:20:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 17943, "name": "h220430"}, {"id": 15521, "name": "Schemata Architects"}, {"id": 17944, "name": "Satoshi Itasaka"}, {"id": 15827, "name": "jaime hayon"}, {"id": 17945, "name": "Kyumin Ha"}, {"id": 17946, "name": "Joey Ruiter"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071057588TGos4bv0uQ7StOM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tTriangle Roomshoes by nendo\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t日本 nendo 工作室的新作是一双拖鞋，看起来像一顶巫师帽，三角形，灰色，可无限重叠，非常干净简单。不仅可以将拖鞋立起来，重叠在一起也很方便收纳。当穿进这些拖鞋里，脚背的布料会呈现自然的褶皱，看起来居家且舒服。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/triangle-roomshoes/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">这里是工作室的主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215040Uz6RJ5dw4YBPf9sc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215040gfGzOs3M7K4Wj1co.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215041CSyOkFtAiloc2G9B.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215042U7wovnNPYL98Sibz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215042YIlvJxcBuSE4spXO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150433GEkX0JCRPlsSuTF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59508547\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tThe Birth chandelier by Satoshi Itasaka\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这盏枝形吊灯来自日本 h220430 设计事务所的 Satoshi Itasaka，灵感源于微弱光线下卵子受孕的瞬间。使用了几十个朝向中心的球形灯泡，相互之间以相同的距离排成一个球体，但光线并不明亮。每一个灯泡都吊上了一根松散的线，更加柔和，有复古的典雅。设计师希望以此能重新发现生命的美妙。感兴趣的话，<a href=\"http://www.h220430.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">可以关注他们其他的作品。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215043LcmuYS8a56CP4BMx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150441Cv9tFxHiEAMyhGd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215044ciXnsMSyKE8e5NLr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215045w3e4CIaluNMd5nTv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.616\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215045ctBqIZ0skerAz5X8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t柯布西耶纪念小件 by Jaime Hayon&amp;卡西纳\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些木制的小物件是为了纪念柯布西耶逝世 50 周年，材料来自一颗种植在莱芒湖畔小别墅（villa “le lac”）庭院露台的泡桐树，因为无法治愈而送到了木工厂。意大利家具品牌卡西纳邀请设计师 Jaime Hayon 创作这组物品，包括鸟居、小鸟和秋千，它们可以用来存放明信片和书本，简单而富有诗意。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150457ASPB2KdtxHZaOnz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150464H9OfMgAxQqozdUW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150488Ts9mAhoBxtMCaQf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215048wPOT906F2aHprotj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215049kyYfR5ZsFB7N6nrS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t工作室桌椅 by Schemata Architects\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这套桌椅来自日本的建筑事务所 Schemata Architects，他们要为一个前身是教室的工作室定制。在四根木制的腿上用了白色的钢管做支撑，更加稳固且显得简洁有序。此外，木材和钢材，浅棕色和白色对比，让这套桌椅看起来很清爽。<a href=\"http://schemata.jp/w-workshop-furniture-for-studio-renova-ring/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215049P0CUdbhTqpYImwaH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215049AhsvF8dURCrDjVzt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215050nufLxkU08BAZ2XRH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215050eAW2fiy4Xgw5xjMP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215051HGWdmnQZ30tg9c4w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tmini washer Machine by Kyumin Ha\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是韩国设计师 Kyumin Ha 设计的小型洗衣机，看上去近似一个榨汁机。上面的圆筒可以加入衣服，下面放水和洗衣液，然后就只需等待了。不过，体积太小也限制了它的功能，不能脱水排水，是一个半自动的洗衣机，因而它更加适合个人清理小型衣物，作为大型洗衣机的附属。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215051UnfDzuokg5L2lipI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.98190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215052iQu57LVNOsJcHnTD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.29619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150524W5n7RLSq1Ke9Cfw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215053LcIVfFDSrOsgE30i.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150533LXyWVBsRjpHdbcC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tInner City Bikes by  Joey Ruiter\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这辆小型自行车 BIG20 来自 Joey Ruiter，它带有一个 1×10 的传动系统，小型的车轮和框架让它几乎是自行车里的极简设计，但也拥有一个直接利落的现代感。因为重量很轻，非常容易携带，骑着它在拥挤的街上穿梭能很好地避开人群并找到停靠的位置。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215054gXSfVFhnmIiZrAp9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215054mLCb4Rvla1iHgKe9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215055OwiaSDTLmJA4H1U8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215055ZeHftXDIyEVbvuPx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521505653PsnGYBZpfXc904.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}